</span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":231,\"repo\":\"node-dmx/dmx\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - DMX controller library for Node.js. <code>nodejs</code> <code>✓ open-source</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-20T15:45:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Graphics</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.gimp.org/\">GIMP</a> - GIMP is a cross-platform image editor available for Linux, Windows, and macOS.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-20T15:45:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://tsp.esta.org/tsp/documents/published_docs.php\">ESTA Technical Standards Program</a> - Collection of technical standards in the entertainment technology industry.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-20T15:45:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Misc/other</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linux\">Linux</a> - A free operating system that can run on pretty much every kind of computer and is great for breathing new life into old computers that aren't supported by the newer Windows editions. There's tons of different distributions to choose from,. The most common one for general computer stuff is <a href=\"https://ubuntu.com/\">Ubuntu</a>. <code>✓ open-source</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-20T15:45:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2><h3>Timecode</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/TheGreyDiamond/Time-MIDI-sender\">Time MIDI sender</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/TheGreyDiamond/Time-MIDI-sender\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">0</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":0,\"repo\":\"TheGreyDiamond/Time-MIDI-sender\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A free tool for sending time data to DasLight (via MIDI). <code>✓ open-source</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-08T08:17:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Resources</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/nodiscc/awesome-linuxaudio\">awesome-linuxaudio</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/nodiscc/awesome-linuxaudio\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1009,\"repo\":\"nodiscc/awesome-linuxaudio\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A Awesome list with all things Linux audio.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-06-08T07:53:57.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Lighting Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.avolites.com/software/downloads/titan-pc-suite\">Avolites Titan</a> - PC version of the Titan software which runs on the Avolites desk. Free to use until version 11.4 although it spits out random data once in a while. Requires a dongle from version 12. <code>⚠ not free</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Lighting Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.etcconnect.com/Products/Consoles/Eos-Family/\">EOS Family</a> - Software for ETC's EOS-family consoles. <code>⚠ freemium</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Lighting Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.malighting.com/downloads/products/grandma2/\">GrandMA2 software</a> - Free, offline software for the GrandMA2 lighting console. Includes GrandMA2 OnPC and MA3D. Does not output DMX for free. <code>⚠ freemium</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Lighting Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.malighting.com/downloads/products/grandma3/\">GrandMA3 software</a> - Free, offline software for the <strong>new</strong> GrandMA3 lighting console. Includes GrandMA3 OnPC. Does not output DMX for free. <code>⚠ freemium</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Lighting Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.highend.com/products/consoles/\">Hog 4 software</a> - Free, offline software for the Hog 4 lighting console. Includes Hog 4 pc. Does not output DMX for free. <code>⚠ freemium</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Lighting Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.qlcplus.org/\">QLC+</a> - QLC+ is a free and cross-platform software to control DMX or analog lighting systems like moving heads, dimmers, scanners etc. <a href=\"https://github.com/mcallegari/qlcplus\">Source Code</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mcallegari/qlcplus\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">594</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":594,\"repo\":\"mcallegari/qlcplus\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> <code>✓ open-source</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Lighting Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://xlights.org/\">xLights</a> - Meant for home Christmas light shows but is a great way to sync lights to music on a budget. <a href=\"https://github.com/smeighan/xLights\">Source Code</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/smeighan/xLights\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">342</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":342,\"repo\":\"smeighan/xLights\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> <code>✓ open-source</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Visualizers</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.capture.se/\">Capture</a> - Documentation and visualisation software. Capture is a native macOS and Windows application that lets you work with lighting, video, laser, moving scenery and water effects. Does have a free Student Edition. <code>⚠ freemium</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Visualizers</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.syncronorm.com/products/depence2/overview/\">Depence²</a> - Depence² is a unique application, which combines the design and visualization process with the potential to control the real show. <code>⚠ not free</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Visualizers</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://cast-soft.com/wysiwyg-lighting-design/\">wysiwyg</a> - wysiwyg is an all-in-one lighting design software with fully integrated CAD, plots, data, visualization and virtual show control. <code>⚠ not free</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Audio Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.audacityteam.org/\">Audacity</a> - Audio file editor and analysis tool, great for cropping down sound effects and music tracks. <code>✓ open-source</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Audio Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://ardour.org/\">Ardour</a> - A full realtime audio recording and editing suite. <a href=\"https://github.com/Ardour/ardour\">Source Code</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Ardour/ardour\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2.7k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":2675,\"repo\":\"Ardour/ardour\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> <code>✓ open-source</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Audio Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.linux-show-player.org/\">Linux Show Player</a> - Free cue player designed for stage productions. <a href=\"https://github.com/FrancescoCeruti/linux-show-player\">Source Code</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/FrancescoCeruti/linux-show-player\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">147</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":147,\"repo\":\"FrancescoCeruti/linux-show-player\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> <code>✓ open-source</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Audio Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://qlab.app/\">QLab</a> - QLab is sound, video, and lighting control for macOS. <code>⚠ freemium</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h3>Audio Software</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.reaper.fm/\">REAPER</a> - REAPER is a complete digital audio production application for computers, offering a full multitrack audio and MIDI recording, editing, processing, mixing and mastering toolset. <code>⚠ freemium</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-05-22T11:41:06.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Netlob/livescript\">Livescript</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Netlob/livescript\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":4,\"repo\":\"Netlob/livescript\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Insert a musical/theatre-script from Google Docs and use this for a live \"autocue\" and scroller wi